---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Odin’s Vault — custom websites & MVP web apps"
  description="We build landing pages, institutional sites, and MVP web apps for small businesses — fast, sharp, and tailored. SC/BR, online worldwide."
>
  <section class="hero2">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="pill">Neon-green speed • Gold-level polish • Zero template vibes</div>

      <h1>
        Your idea didn’t come here to be <span style="color:var(--neon); text-shadow:0 0 26px rgba(57,255,20,0.22);">average</span>.
      </h1>

      <p class="sub">
        Odin’s Vault builds <b>custom</b> websites and MVP web apps for small businesses.
        If you’re tired of “play by the rules” agencies, welcome — we ship <b>novel</b>, <b>clean</b>, and <b>fast</b>.
      </p>

      <div class="btnrow">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://calendly.com/your-next-devops/quick-chat" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Book a quick chat</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="https://wa.me/5548998142779" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">WhatsApp</a>
      </div>

      <div class="statrow" aria-label="Quick stats">
        <div class="stat"><b>Productized MVP</b><span>clear scope, fast delivery</span></div>
        <div class="stat"><b>AI-accelerated</b><span>less busywork, more value</span></div>
        <div class="stat"><b>SC/BR • Online</b><span>Brazil + worldwide</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="features">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="kicker">Features</div>
      <h2>Custom doesn’t mean slow</h2>
      <p class="sub" style="max-width:820px;">
        We don’t “sell templates”. We ship your product with a cyber-vault aesthetic, high contrast,
        and the kind of confidence that makes customers think: <i>“holy sh*t, I found the right person.”</i>
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-3" style="margin-top:18px;">
        <div class="card"><h3>Fast delivery</h3><p>AI + sane tooling. Less ceremony, more shipping.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3>Conversion-ready</h3><p>Copy structure + hierarchy that guides decisions.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3>Mobile-first</h3><p>Looks sharp on phones without “responsive surprises”.</p></div>

        <div class="card"><h3>Performance minded</h3><p>Static-first when possible. Minimal JS. Quick loads.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3>Easy handoff</h3><p>GitHub Pages today, scalable hosting tomorrow.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3>No maintenance trap</h3><p>We leverage SaaS smartly so you don’t babysit infra.</p></div>

        <div class="card"><h3>Analytics (GA)</h3><p>Track what matters. Improve what works.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3>SEO basics</h3><p>Metadata, structure, and pages that search engines can read.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3>Brand vibe</h3><p>Avant-garde, tech, trend — without being cringe.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="how">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="kicker">How it works</div>
      <h2>From “in the drawer” to live</h2>
      <p class="sub" style="max-width:820px;">
        Some ideas are born mediocre. Yours isn’t. We move fast, keep you in control, and avoid fake complexity.
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-3" style="margin-top:18px;">
        <div class="card"><h3>1) Align</h3><p>We clarify goal, audience, and the one metric that matters.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3>2) Design + Copy</h3><p>We shape the story: value, proof, and a clean call-to-action.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3>3) Build</h3><p>Astro static site + modern components. Fast, secure, boring to host.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3>4) Iterate</h3><p>We polish details: spacing, responsiveness, performance, SEO.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3>5) Launch</h3><p>GitHub Pages deploy + tracking (GA) + a simple handoff.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3>6) Grow</h3><p>When you’re ready: MVP web app, integrations, automation.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="testimonials">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="kicker">Proof</div>
      <h2>Testimonials & screenshots</h2>
      <p class="sub" style="max-width:820px;">
        Placeholder page for now — you’ll paste real client stories soon.
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-3" style="margin-top:18px;">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="quote">“If it was meant to be like everyone else, you wouldn’t be building yours.”</div>
          <div class="who">— Placeholder • 2026</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="quote">“Some ideas are born mediocre. Yours isn’t.”</div>
          <div class="who">— Placeholder • 2026</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="quote">“Everyone is afraid. The ones who face it win.”</div>
          <div class="who">— Placeholder • 2026</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-top:14px;">
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href={`${Astro.base}/proof`}>Open the Proof page</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="pricing">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="kicker">Services</div>
      <h2>Productized offers (MVP-friendly)</h2>
      <p class="sub" style="max-width:820px;">
        Clear outcomes. Clear scope. If you want custom beyond this — that’s the fun part.
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-3" style="margin-top:18px;">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Landing Page</h3>
          <p>Single-page, conversion-focused. Perfect for new offers and campaigns.</p>
          <div style="margin-top:12px;"><span class="pill">Fastest path to live</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Institutional Site</h3>
          <p>Multi-page brand site: About, Services, Tech, Proof, Contact. Clean and credible.</p>
          <div style="margin-top:12px;"><span class="pill">Brand authority</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>MVP Web App + Landing</h3>
          <p>Validate the product: auth, core flows, and a landing page to sell it.</p>
          <div style="margin-top:12px;"><span class="pill">Build the real thing</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-top:14px;">
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href={`${Astro.base}/services`}>See details</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="faq">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="kicker">FAQ</div>
      <h2>Direct answers</h2>

      <div class="grid grid-2" style="margin-top:18px;">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>“Isn’t this too complicated?”</h3>
          <p>No. Most “complexity” is agencies selling fear. We keep the stack boring and the product sharp.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>“Can I ask for something weird?”</h3>
          <p>Please. Normal is everywhere. We collect treasures.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>“Do you do maintenance?”</h3>
          <p>We prefer to reduce it. We use SaaS and static hosting whenever it makes sense.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>“Can you work with my content?”</h3>
          <p>Yes. You bring text/screenshots. We shape it into a story that converts.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="contact" style="padding-bottom:110px;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="kicker">Get started</div>
      <h2>Let’s build your treasure</h2>
      <p class="sub" style="max-width:820px;">
        If you’re ready to stop hearing “it has to follow the rules”, book a quick chat or ping me on WhatsApp.
      </p>

      <div class="contactbox" style="margin-top:18px;">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://calendly.com/your-next-devops/quick-chat" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Calendly — quick chat</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="https://wa.me/5548998142779" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">WhatsApp — +55 48 99814-2779</a>
      </div>

      <p class="small" style="margin-top:14px; color: rgba(231,234,243,0.62);">
        Location: SC / Brazil • Available online worldwide • Google Analytics supported (set <code>PUBLIC_GA_ID</code>).
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
